results.t: Neil Buchanan: Former Art Attack host denies Banksy ...
results.p: Sep 7, 2020 — It came after a social media rumour suggested the former Art Attack and Finder's Keepers host was the man behind Banksy's anonymous street art.

results.t: Iconic 90s show Art Attack is returning with brand new host
results.p: Jul 23, 2024 — Art Attack was a rage in the 90s and it will soon be back on our screens with a brand new host - and he's someone we all know and love...
Join Lloyd and Alex the Big Artist for Art Attack, the Big Art Show that proves you don't have to be a great artist, to be great at Art!
Art Attack is a British children's television series revolving around art. running from 1990 to 2007, and was presented throughout by Neil Buchanan.
